@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5249

### GraphQL - All stations
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ stations { id name location { city state latitude longitude elevationFt } status } }"}

### GraphQL - Filter stations by state
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ stations(state: \"FL\") { id name location { city state } } }"}

### GraphQL - Current conditions (nested types)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ currentConditions(stationId: \"mia01\") { observedAt temperatureF feelsLikeF humidityPercent dewPointF pressureMb skyCondition uvIndex wind { speedMph direction gustsMph } precipitation { type amountInches probabilityPercent } } }"}

### GraphQL - Current conditions in Celsius
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ currentConditions(stationId: \"den01\", unit: CELSIUS) { temperatureF feelsLikeF dewPointF skyCondition } }"}

### GraphQL - 3-day daily forecast
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ dailyForecast(stationId: \"chi01\", days: 3) { date highTempF lowTempF skyCondition wind { speedMph direction gustsMph } precipitation { type probabilityPercent } sunrise sunset } }"}

### GraphQL - Hourly forecast (next 6 hours)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ hourlyForecast(stationId: \"phx01\", hours: 6) { dateTime temperatureF feelsLikeF skyCondition wind { speedMph direction } precipitation { probabilityPercent } } }"}

### GraphQL - Active alerts (all)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ activeAlerts { id title severity category affectedArea issuedAt expiresAt description } }"}

### GraphQL - Alerts filtered by severity
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ activeAlerts(minSeverity: WARNING) { id title severity category affectedArea } }"}

### GraphQL - Alerts for a specific station
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ activeAlerts(stationId: \"chi01\") { id title severity category } }"}

### GraphQL - Air quality
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"{ airQuality(stationId: \"phx01\") { aqi category primaryPollutant pollutants { key value } } }"}

